::Feline::

She walked around mapping out the ship and putting it to memory.  She 
came up upon the bridge. She stood in the doorway and looked around. 
Just in case someone asked, she was lost. That story would work since 
she was new to the ship anyway. She would deffinately have to ask for 
a tour of the ship.  She took a step inside the bridge and leaned 
against the wall.  She swayed her tail around and looked around, 
taking in the sights.  She purred and smiled. This may be and easy 
assignment after all. 

She thought of Skulletron. She hoped he was having fun where ever he 
was.
